      "author": "dsokolov",
      "description": "# Release Notes for v0.3.1\r\n\r\n**Major Update: Complete Rewrite with Enhanced Features**\r\n\r\n## ✨ **New Features**\r\n- **Coordinate labels** - Show/hide board coordinates\r\n- **Hoshi (star points)** - Traditional Go board markings\r\n- **Multiple board sizes** - Support for 3x3 to 19x19 boards\r\n- **Russian documentation** - Full localization support\r\n\r\n## 🏗️ **Architecture**\r\n- **Complete codebase rewrite** with modular design\r\n- **Dependency injection** for better maintainability\r\n- **Comprehensive test suite** with visual regression testing\r\n\r\n## 🎨 **Improvements**\r\n- **Better rendering** with improved spacing and margins\r\n- **Enhanced color schemes** with system color support\r\n- **Updated dependencies** and build configuration\r\n\r\nThis release transforms GoBoard into a robust, well-tested plugin with a solid foundation for future development.\r\n",
