      "description": "# GoBoard Plugin v0.2.0 Release Notes\r\n\r\n## 🎉 What's New\r\n\r\n**GoBoard v0.2.0** introduces interactive stone placement, support for hoshi (star points), and seamless theme integration with Obsidian. The plugin now automatically adapts to your light/dark theme and provides real-time diagram updates when settings change. Major architectural improvements include a service-oriented design with specialized modules for better performance and maintainability. Fixed coordinate system issues and improved the overall user experience with enhanced toolbar design and better settings organization.\r\n",
