      "author": "dsokolov",
      "description": "# GoBoard Plugin - Release Notes v0.1.0\r\n\r\n## 🎉 Initial Release\r\n\r\n**GoBoard** is an Obsidian plugin that renders Go game diagrams from markdown code blocks using the `goboard` language identifier. The plugin supports 9x9, 13x13, and 19x19 boards with customizable appearance, stone colors, and optional coordinate display. All settings are configurable through Obsidian's plugin settings panel with real-time updates.\r\n",
      "downloadCount": 3,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "v0.1.0",
